Reasoning: The paper discusses the use of a first-order logic reasoning system in combination with a knowledge base to create an artificial consciousness system. This falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and logic in computer science (cs.LO). The use of a knowledge base also relates to computational complexity (cs.CC) and natural language processing (cs.CL). Finally, the discussion of consciousness and mind wandering could also be relevant to cognitive science (cs.CY).
